features: 【Extended Handrail & Safety Guarantee】For the elderly to use walking treadmill, the most important issue is safety. For this purpose, we have designed the following. Use the multi-grip handrails that sit along the top, middle, and end of the low-deck treadmill for extra support, to avoid falling due to an unstable center of gravity. In the event of an accidental fall, the safety key will immediately drop to disconnect the power supply.

【No More Excuses for Not Exercising】As we age we want to maintain our mobility as much as possible. But on the way to staying healthy, bad weather is always the best excuse for everyone not to exercise. Owning this walking machines for exercise, weather is no longer a reason, you can walk every day. In order to ensure that the workout does not damage the knee, a six-layer thickened running belt and a super shock absorption system are used.

【Easy to Operate LCD Display】Seniors/convalescents can clearly keep track of all their progress with backlit screens that measure distance walked, calories burned, heart rate, speed, and more. They can also easily operate our recovery exercise treadmill with simple buttons and no bells and whistles. If there are young people at home who are willing to use it, the home gym treadmill also has 12 preset modes to choose. Phone & water cup holder are also designed.

【Stronger Motor & Structure】Walk and jog between 0.5mph and 5.5 mph by using the 2.25-peak horsepower motor on the indoor high weight capacity treadmill. Super powerful motor means quiet and more enjoyment of sports. Compared with other ordinary motorized treadmills, it is speed increment of 0.1mph for better adaptation. Premium materials and stable construction, supports up to 300 lb.

【Suitable for Home Use】 If there are other members of the family who want to use it and feel that the armrest is a little restrictive, it can be removed, which does not affect use. And after disassembly, the treadmill can be folded. What’s more, this portable treadmill can be moved from room to room with its transportation wheels. The folded size doesn't take up much space.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
STAND-TDML4 
Height Adjustable Laptop Desk for Treadmill 
Do you feel rushed for time and unable to get the exercise you need? This innovative design, fitting most laptops and treadmills on the market, allows you to get your work done while walking, making it possible to study, do homework, research, shop, and more while on the move. Routine exercise increases energy and boosts your mood, not to mention you can double your walking time while you knock out your to-do list. With this stand's sturdy wooden tray, adjustable bracket width (Velcro straps are 15.3" in length), ergonomic tilt, and height adjustment, you can secure your laptop to the treadmill and find just the right viewing angle every time! 
᷾ 
SPECS: 
Material: Particle Board, Steel
Tray Dimensions: 26.9” x 11” (2 sections)
Handlebar Distance: 27" to 40"
Velcro Strap Length: 15.3" (each)
Tray Tilt: 0° to -25°
Height Adjustment: Provided along the 14” pole
Mouse Pad Dimensions: 7” x 5.9”
Wrist Pad Length: 23.7” (total)
INNOVATIVE DESIGN 
Simple to Use - Turns your laptop into a walking desk with the addition of this laptop stand that secures tightly to your treadmill’s handlebars. 
Adjustable - Tooless width and height adjustment make it possible to match the distance between your handlebars and find a comfortable viewing angle. 
Padding - Mouse pad increases traction on the particle board surface, and wrist padding provides excellent wrist support. 
COMPATIBILITY 
Universal Design: Made to fit most sizes of laptops and most types of treadmills on the market
Maximum Handlebar Diameter: 9.4"
Weight Capacity: 8.8 lbs
SIMPLE ASSEMBLY 
Assemble Adjustment Bracket 
First, remove the thumbscrews and end caps from the center brace and insert the brace into the adjustment bracket. Then, insert the end caps into the crossbars, slide them into the center brace, and reinsert the thumbscrews. 
Install Keyboard Tray 
Next, attach the support plate to the center pole using the provided hardware. Then, mount the keyboard tray to the support plate and tighten in place. You’re almost there! 
Attach Padding 
Remove the adhesive backing from the wrist pads and place them on the front edge of the keyboard tray. This will help support your wrists and provide a safety lip for your laptop. 
Secure to Handlebars 
Lastly, insert the center pole into the adjustment bracket, loosen the thumbscrews on the center brace, and adjust the crossbars to fit your treadmill. Tightly fasten the mount to the treadmill’s handlebars and adjust to desired height.

title: Peloton Tread | Treadmill for Running, Walking, and Hiking with Manual or Auto-Incline Options and Immersive 24” HD Touchscreen
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Cardio Training › Treadmills
description: Peloton Tread, Treadmill for Running, Walking and Hiking with Immersive 24” HD Touchscreen The Peloton Tread brings a studio experience home. Get a powerful cardio workout with a 24" HD touchscreen with front and rear-facing speakers. Unlock thousands of classes, both on and off the Tread, like running, walking, hiking, or Tread Bootcamp. When rest days come around, you can balance running and strength with yoga, meditation and stretching. Explore our lineup of 50+ instructors, and track your progress class after class using on-screen metrics. Your Peloton Tread is compatible with any ANT+ heart rate monitor, Apple Watch®, Strava, or any Android watch running Wear OS 3 or higher. Set up one-tap fitness tracking to monitor your heart rate and close your rings. All-Access Membership must be purchased separately in order to access Peloton classes on your Tread. You’ll pay one monthly fee for your entire household (Age, height and weight restrictions apply.) so everyone can access our entire library of classes that range from 5 to 90 minutes. With workouts that fit your experience level, mood, goals, music style, and schedule, you’ll be ready to train on and off your Peloton Tread or move anytime, anywhere with the Peloton App.
features: VALUE-PACKED MEMBERSHIP: A Peloton All-Access Membership must be purchased separately in order to access Peloton content on your Tread. You’ll pay $44/mo for your entire household and get unlimited access to our entire library of content available on your Tread and the Peloton App. Age, height, and weight restrictions apply. Your account can be activated on the touch screen during Tread assembly.

THOUSANDS OF LIVE & ON-DEMAND CLASSES: Access to thousands of classes, both on and off your Tread, like running, walking, hiking, strength, bootcamp, yoga, and more. To customize your workouts, Peloton allows you to stack classes, enabling you to transition from class to class with ease

IMMERSIVE, INTUITIVE RUNNING AND WALKING EXPERIENCE: Speed and incline knobs allow you to easily adjust controls without breaking your stride, or use auto-incline to automatically follow instructor cues up or downhill Use captions or receive spoken feedback from the Peloton Tread touchscreen with TalkBack Knobs with jump buttons.

On-screen shortcuts allow you to change speeds from 0 to 12.5 MPH and incline grades from 0% to 12.5% Clip-on the safety key while running and the belt will come to a quick stop if detached. Lock your Tread with a passcode when not in use

TRACK YOUR PROGRESS & METRICS: A wide-range of on-screen, real-time metrics enable you track progress, streaks and performance across workouts Follow training programs, or set personal targets during a freestyle workout, to help you meet your running and strength goals

CONNECT TO YOUR TRAINING DEVICES: Easily connect any ANT+ heart rate monitor, Apple Watch and Strava to your Peloton Tread to capture performance data, including Strive Score, an in-class metric on heart rate zones, from your workouts and track fitness goals

SPACE TO RUN ON A COMPACT FOOTPRINT: The Peloton Tread has a compact 5½' x 2¾' footprint that still has plenty of room for running and walking on its 59” textured, comfortable and quiet running belt Get a powerful cardio workout in less space than your average treadmill We recommend at least 24” of space to the left, right and front of the Tread, and 79” of space in the back for storing and training The ceiling height minimum is 20” greater than the user’s height

title: The Valuation Treadmill: How Securities Fraud Threatens the Integrity of Public Companies
author: James J. Park
breadCrumbs: Kindle Store › Kindle eBooks › Law

attributes.value: Up to 4 simultaneous devices, per publisher limits

bookDescription: Public companies now face constant pressure to meet investor expectations. A company must continually deliver strong short-term performance every quarter to maintain its stock price. This valuation treadmill creates incentives for corporations to deceive investors. Published more than twenty years after the passage of Sarbanes-Oxley, which requires all public companies to invest in measures to ensure the accuracy of their disclosures, The Valuation Treadmill shows how securities fraud became a major regulatory concern. Drawing on case studies of paradigmatic securities enforcement actions involving Xerox, Penn Central, Apple, Enron, Citigroup, and General Electric, the book argues that corporate securities fraud emerged as investors increasingly valued companies based on their future performance. Corporations now have an incentive to issue unrealistically optimistic disclosure to convince markets that their success will continue. Securities regulation must do more to protect the integrity of public companies from the pressure of the valuation treadmill.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Treadmill maintenance may be needed to keep your exercise equipment working, but doing it can certainly can feel like a chore. Apart from all the time it takes, loosening and tightening components on the machinery can lead to it being damaged, meaning you risk doing more harm than good every time you lubricate… 
Thankfully, Noosa Life are here to make these problems a thing of the past with this essential lubricant with time-saving applicator. Effectively lubricate your treadmill in seconds - without any disassembly - by using the applicator to apply it directly to the middle of the belt! 
Enjoy effortless high quality USA-made lubricating action with Noosa Life. 
Easy-Use Treadmill Maintenance Accessory 
This lubricant was specially made to take the stress and mess out of treadmill maintenance. Simply insert the custom created applicator beneath the treadmill and squeeze for effortless lubrication - all without loosening or removing any components! 
Apply your new lubricant regularly for effective treadmill maintenance that can be completed in a matter of seconds. 
Made In The USA 
Competitors may be happy to source their lubricant from the cheapest option overseas, but here at Noosa Life we ensure all our lubricant is USA-made. 
Enjoy 100% silicone treadmill lubricant safe in the knowledge every batch is carefully monitored for purity, effect and performance! 
Unique Safe-Close Applicator 
Tired of applicators leaking, getting clogged up or simply being unsuitable for even steady application? 
Then enjoy using the unique applicator on this lubricant, complete with a safe-close design that can be closed for secure lubricant storage when not in use. 
Non-Toxic Odorless Formula 
Our lubricant is made to be safely non-toxic with zero propellants. 
Better still, our totally odorless formula means you can do maintenance without suffering through the nasty smell so many other competing lubricants have. 
Featured On Major News Outlets 
Our treadmill lubricant is so impressive it’s been featured on a number of major news networks, including NBC, ABC, Fox and the Boston Herald. Buy your treadmill lubricant with total confidence today!

features: [Value-packed membership] A Peloton All-Access Membership must be purchased separately in order to access Peloton content on your Bike+. NEW AND IMPROVED FEATURES: Releasing updates and new features based on Member feedback ensures you have the tools to stay focused and meet your goals. ON SCREEN CONTROLS: Use Auto-resistance when you want and easily turn it off when you don’t with a tap of the lock icon. [Find, plan, and customize workouts] CUSTOM-BUILD YOUR WORKOUT: Line up classes and easily go from one to the next with Stacked Classes. [Monitor heart rate, workout performance, and more] CONNECT HEART RATE MONITORS: Easily connect any ANT+ heart rate monitor to your Peloton Bike+. TRACK PERFORMANCE: Pair your Apple or Wear OS watch to the Peloton Watch App to track heart rate and workout metrics in any class. REAL-TIME METRICS: See in-class metrics like cadence, output, resistance, heart rate, distance and more.

[On screen metrics] TRACK PROGRESS OVER TIME: Check workout streaks, personal bests, goals achieved, and more. LEADERBOARD: See who’s in class, give out high-fives, and chase others up the Leaderboard for some friendly competition.

[Workout in compact spaces and beyond] 4’x2’ FOOTPRINT: Peloton Bike+ only needs the space the size of a small yoga mat. WORKOUTS BEYOND BIKE+: Add on strength, yoga, HIIT, and more off to the side of Peloton Bike+ or anywhere you’d like using Peloton App, included with All-Access Membership.

Use lifting aids and proper lifting techniques when moving or assembling the Peloton Bike+. A second person may be helpful when raising and lowering the Bike+. Lifting heavy objects can cause muscle strain and back injuries. Heavy objects can also fall and cause injury and physical damage.

title: Treadmill: A Novel
author: Hiroshi Nakamura
breadCrumbs: Books › Literature & Fiction › Genre Fiction
bookDescription: Treadmill is a truly unique and historically significant novel and the only book written about life in the Japanese-American internment camps during World War II written at the time by an internee.Hiroshi Nakamura, along with his family, spent the war years in Salinas Assembly Center, Salinas, California; Camp II of the Poston Relocation Center, Parker, Arizona; and Tule Lake Segregation Center, Newell, California. It was during this period that he put down on paper what he was observing, experiencing, and hearing and expressed them in this novel. Nakamura captures exquisitely the thinking and mood of the people. It accurately evokes the fears, anxieties, suspicions, cynicisms and passions brought out by camp life. Nakamura ‘almost' succeeded in getting Treadmill published in the late 1940s. While editors and publishers thought well of the novel, they would not publish it as it was ‘too sensitive' an issue. Professor Peter Suzuki discovered Treadmill while he was doing some research on internment camps of Japanese Americans.This revised edition of Treadmill contains a new introductory essay by Professor Tara Fickle discussing the historical importance of Nakamura's work. Also included are a series of photographs of Japanese internment camps in California taken by renowned photographer Ansel Adams taken in 1943. Adams had unprecedented access to life inside the camps and these photographs provide an exceptional visual accompaniment to Nakamura's story.

title: Treadmill of Production: Injustice and Unsustainability in the Global Economy (Advancing the Sociological Imagination Series)
inStockText: In Stock  Only 1 left in stock - order soon.
author: Kenneth A. Gould
breadCrumbs: Books › Politics & Social Sciences › Politics & Government
bookDescription: Schnaiberg's concept of the treadmill of production is arguably the most visible and enduring theory to emerge in three decades of environmental sociology. Elaborated and tested, it has been found to be an accurate predictor of political-economic changes in the global economy. In the global South, it has figures prominently in the work of structural environmental analysts and has been used by many political-economic movements. Building new extensions and applications of the treadmill theory, this new book shows how and why northern analysts and governments have failed to protect our environment and secure our future. Using an empirically based political-economic perspective, the authors outline the causes of environmental degradation, the limits of environmental protection policies, and the failures of institutional decision-makers to protect human well-being.

title: On the Treadmill to Pearl Harbor: The Memoirs of Admiral James O. Richardson
author: George C. Dyer
breadCrumbs: Kindle Store › Kindle eBooks › History
bookDescription: Endless debates have raged over the reasons the Japanese were able to execute their surprise attack on the U.S. Navy's Pacific Fleet at Pearl Harbor so successfully. Military neglect, political and diplomatic ineptitude, and even what could only be described as accusations of malfeasance against the President of the United States all have been argued and reargued for more than 60 years. One key source of information for this ongoing and sometime passionate discussion is "On the Treadmill to Pearl Harbor: the Memoirs of Admiral James O. Richardson." As commander of the U.S. Fleet in 1940 and 1941, Admiral Richardson was in a unique position to observe and reach conclusions about the readiness or lack of readiness of the fleet, as well as the political atmosphere in which crucial strategic and tactical decisions were reached. Because many crucial naval records perished at Pearl Harbor, Admiral Richardson's recollections, as told to Rear Admiral George C. Dyer, constitute an important primary source for war plans, including War Plan Orange for operations in case of a war with Japan. He also addresses his deep concern about the lack of preparedness of the Navy, particularly its low prewar staffing levels, and the folly of sending a poorly prepared naval force to Pearl Harbor as a deterrent to aggression by a better prepared Japanese fleet. He forthrightly places much of the blamed for this situation on President Roosevelt and his advisers. Interestingly, in light of the many conspiracy theories surrounding December 7, 1941, he criticizes these men for consistently underestimating the Japanese threat rather than courting an attack as a way of embroiling the U.S. in the war. On the Treadmill to Pearl Harbor is an important source for naval historians and students of World War II, as well as an intriguing first-person account of the crucial months preceding "the day of infamy."

description: Introducing the SereneLife 2-in-1 Foldable Treadmill & Walking Pad, a versatile and innovative fitness solution for both home and office environments. This multifunctional treadmill can be used as a walking or jogging pad with speeds ranging from 0.6-5 MPH when the handrail is down, or as a full-speed running treadmill with speeds up to 8.7 MPH when the handrail is raised. Powered by a robust 2.5HP motor, it supports users up to 265 lbs and provides a comfortable workout experience with its advanced shock absorption system and a large 43 x 15-inch running area. The treadmill offers 12 pre-set training modes, adjustable speed, and a timer, allowing users to tailor their workouts to their specific fitness goals. The included remote control ensures easy access to all settings, making adjustments during your workout effortless. Thanks to its seamless Bluetooth connectivity, you can pair the treadmill with popular fitness apps like Fit Home, Kinomap, and Zwift to track your progress, enjoy interactive workout sessions, and listen to your favorite music. Designed with a compact and foldable frame, the SereneLife Treadmill is perfect for small spaces and can be stored easily when not in use. features: DUAL-MODE DESIGN – Use as a walking or jogging pad (0.6-5 MPH) with the riser folded, or elevate the handrail to reach up to 8.7 MPH, perfect for low-impact exercises and intense workouts. Adapt to your fitness needs with ease.

POWERFUL MOTOR & STURDY BUILD – Features a 2.5HP motor with a weight capacity of up to 265 lbs. The 15.74” x 43.3”-inch belt and shock-absorbing design ensure comfort and stability during use. Enjoy smooth and quiet operation.

SPACE-SAVING, PORTABLE DESIGN – Foldable with built-in wheels for easy storage under desks or beds. Perfect for home offices, apartments, and compact spaces. Easily move and store the treadmill when not in use.

Is it reasonable to cut this to size? Can you get a clean edge with a razor knife? 
Yes. If you use a straight edge you can certainly cut to size. While it’s a nice thickness, it’s definitely soft enough to cut cleanly with sharp razor.

author: David Siik
breadCrumbs: Books › Sports & Outdoors › Individual Sports
bookDescription: As seen on Fox News, Instyle.com, and in Self Magazine & Women's Running Maximize the burn and eliminate the pain with the BITE method!Move over, HIIT--there's a new workout in town! The Balanced Interval Training Experience, or BITE method, helps you shed weight and improve your run faster than ever before. Based on David Siik's award-winning methodology and experience as an elite runner, fitness instructor, and celebrity trainer, this new running program strikes an ingenious middle ground between sprinting and distance training.With a signature formula and flow, Siik's BITE method provides you with the most incredible workout you've ever had on a treadmill. His detailed regime takes all the guesswork out of how fast to go, at what incline, and for how long, so that you can just focus on your run. In a few short weeks, you'll find yourself burning fat, losing weight, and boosting your speed just by following these simple principles.No matter what level you're at, The Ultimate Treadmill Workout will help you ramp up your fitness routine, surpass your goals, and achieve the physique you've always wanted!

features: 【SPACIOUS 20-INCH RUNNING DECK】55 x 20-inch running space, offering ample room for a wide range of activities, ensuring a comfortable and accommodating workout experience for users of all sizes.

【15 INCLINE LEVELS & CONVENIENT CONTROLS】Enhance your fitness journey with 15 automatic incline levels on this treadmill, designed to elevate your training with ease. Quick-access buttons, effortlessly adjust the incline for a more intensity.

【ADVANCED BRUSHLESS MOTOR TECHNOLOGY】Experience the efficiency of a brushless motor that delivers a faster, friction-free operation, ensuring a quieter and smoother run. This cutting-edge motor supports speeds ranging from 0.6 to 12 mph.

【24 PERSONALIZED WORKOUT PROGRAMS】Accommodate up to three user profiles and store 24 tailor-made workout routines to match the unique fitness levels of each user. Progress from beginner to advanced levels, enhancing calorie burn with intensity.

【CONNECTED FITNESS】Elevate workouts with the FREE SunnyFit app. Bluetooth sync offers 1,000+ trainer-led videos, 10,000+ tours, and diverse programs. Personalize training, track progress, and join community challenges on your treadmill.

【ADVANCED DIGITAL MONITOR】This performance digital monitor features a large, backlit LED screen for effortless viewing of essential workout metrics, including heart rate time, distance, calories, speed, and steps. Enjoy real-time insights.

【EASY SPEED SELECTION & PULSE SENSORS】Convenient quick-access buttons for instant speed adjustments to 3mph & 6mph, with a top speed of 12 mph to cater to both beginners & advanced runners. Treadmill includes pulse sensors for heart rate tracking.

【ADVANCED DOUBLE DECK DESIGN & SHOCK ABSORPTION】Our treadmill features a cushioned double deck with integrated shock absorption, ensuring a low-impact, stable workout. Supports up to 300 LB, protecting joints for all fitness levels.

【EASY SET-UP & FOLDABLE DESIGN】Assemble in just 20 minutes, featuring a soft hydraulic drop mechanism for safe, hands-free folding and unfolding. With built-in transport wheels, moving and storing this compact treadmill is a breeze.

【OVER 20 YEARS OF EXCELLENCE】Sunny Health & Fitness delivers top-notch equipment dedicated to excellence. With our devoted support team and certified trainers, enjoy an unmatched FIT FOR EVERYONE experience.

author: Charles Miske
breadCrumbs: Kindle Store › Kindle eBooks › Sports & Outdoors

bookDescription: Before you try the brand new Social Media Sensation 12-3-30 You Must Read This Book This short guide answers the question: How do I begin to train cardio with a weighted backpack on an inclined treadmill? Who needs this book? You need this book if you need a super effective low impact cardio workout you can do daily. Walking on an incline with a weighted backpack is scientifically proven to boost fat burning with a simple to follow low impact training program. This simple guide provides the basics necessary to take your training to a new level without overwhelming you with complicated training protocols. If you've been dreading the treadmill, don't see the success you desperately desire, keep getting injured when trying to run on the treadmill, this simple guide is for you. Without complicated charts, or training programs, it's the easiest way to get into the groove and start seeing success. On Social: "Thank you! Your book is fantastic. . . Great work! Its extremely entertaining (so not dry) and sticks to the basics so keeps a newbie from being overwhelmed." Note: Rucking is a common slang term for simply walking with a backpack.

The SereneLife Smart Digital Treadmill Machine is an excellent choice for fitness enthusiasts who have little time to go to the gym, with this home exercise trainer you will be able to achieve your dream body at the comfort of your own home! With this treadmill, your home becomes an ideal gym for you to stay in shape. SereneLife SLFTRD20 features a stylish contemporary space-saving folding design with reliable, sturdy frame for easy storage. 
It features a powerful but quiet motor that is strong enough to hold long distance running sessions and versatile to meet different needs for all of your family members, a useful display to help you track time, calories, distance, speed, and heart rate. It also pairs to your device via Bluetooth, download the 'FitShow App' and get connected to record and review training data, display training stats and challenge friends, and share fitness data on social media. Works with iPhone and Android phones.
